Information for the evaluation shall include, but is not limited to, the following:
The total number of alcohol and drug abuse clients admitted to treatment;
The total number of referrals from the District and Circuit Courts and the Department of Corrections;
The client's change in alcohol and other drug use patterns from admission to discharge from treatment;
The client's change in employment status from admission to discharge from treatment; and
The client's change in involvement with the criminal justice system from admission to discharge from treatment.
